New Balance 550 Sea Salt Burgundy
results.story: The New Balance 550 ‘Burgundy’ delivers a simplistic two-tone colorway of a vintage silhouette originally designed for the ‘80s hardwood. The low-top utilizes a white leather upper with a tonal suede forefoot overlay and padded mesh collar. Contrasting burgundy accents land on the leather collar overlay and heel clip, as well as well as the various branding elements. The sneaker is mounted on a durable rubber cupsole, fitted with an EVA wedge for lightweight cushioning.
